Ro-bat bottles avoidance experiment:

1. Position the bottles on the arena 
2. Switch on Ro-bat
3. Connect 9V battery
5. Connect your PC to wifi Cyber-Physical-Systems with Pw: Torweg-Sisal2-Hm
4. Open SSH connection to the robot:
	> ssh robat@134.34.226.208
	> robat@134.34.226.208's password:thymio
	> conda activate robat
	> /home/robat/miniforge3/envs/robat/bin/python /home/robat/robat_v2/useful_code/obstacle_avoidance.py
	
	ctrl+c to stop it
	


SonoRo experiments:

1. Switch on sonoRos and position them on the arena
2. Connect your PC to wifi Cyber-Physical-Systems with Pw: Torweg-Sisal2-Hm
4. Open SSH connection to the robot:
	> ssh ssh thymio@134.34.226.238 
	
	( Do the same for 134.34.226.240, 134.34.226.241 )
	
	> thymio@134.34.226.238's password:thymio
	> conda activate robat
	
	AGGREGATION
	
	> python /home/thymio/robat_py/robat_swarm/passive_robat/Scripts/robatv1_2_aggregation.py
	
	DISPERSION
	
	> python /home/thymio/robat_py/robat_swarm/passive_robat/Scripts/robatv1_2_dispersion.py
	
	ctrl+c to stop it
		
